:[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Lazer o'ymakorlik sovg'alar: to'liq qo'llanma — Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/lazer-oymakorlik-sovgalar\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Lazer o'ymakorlik sovg'alar haqida ishni qayerdan boshlash kerak?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Kampaniya maqsadi, maqsadli auditoriya va har bir qabul qiluvchi uchun belgilangan byudjetdan boshlang.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Ishga tushirishni ko'pincha nima to'xtatib qo'yadi?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Maketni kech tasdiqlash, segmentlar bo'yicha ustuvorliklarning yo'qligi va kelishilmagan logistika rejasi.\"}}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik sovg&#x27;alar: to&#x27;liq qo&#x27;llanma — Graver.uz</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik sovg&#x27;alar: to&#x27;liq qo&#x27;llanma — Graver.uz</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-01-20\">19-yanvar, 2026</time><span>2<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/lazer-oymakorlik-sovgalar.jpg\" alt=\"Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik sovg&#x27;alar: to&#x27;liq qo&#x27;llanma — Graver.uz\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik — korporativ sovg&#x27;alarni shaxsiylashtirish va brendingiz haqida barqaror taassurot yaratishning eng samarali usullaridan biri. Ushbu qo&#x27;llanmada B2B-jamoasi o&#x27;ymakor sovg&#x27;alarni muvaffaqiyatli ishga tushirish uchun bilishi kerak bo&#x27;lgan hamma narsani ko&#x27;rib chiqamiz.</p>\n<h2>Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik nima?</h2>\n<p>Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik — yuqori aniqlikdagi lazer nuri yordamida material yuzasiga tasvirlar, matn yoki logotiplarni qo&#x27;llash jarayoni. Bosib chiqarish yoki stikerlardan farqli o&#x27;laroq, o&#x27;ymakorlik doimiy bo&#x27;lib, vaqt o&#x27;tishi bilan o&#x27;chmaydi.</p>\n<p><strong>Asosiy afzalliklari:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Uzoq muddatlilik — tasvir so&#x27;nmaydi va o&#x27;chmaydi</li>\n<li>Aniqlik — logotipning eng kichik tafsilotlarini takrorlash</li>\n<li>Premium ko&#x27;rinish — sifat va eksklyuzivlik hissini yaratadi</li>\n<li>Ko&#x27;p qirralilik — metall, yog&#x27;och, teri, shishada ishlaydi</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Qaysi materiallar o&#x27;ymakorlik uchun mos keladi?</h2>\n<h3>Metall</h3>\n<p>Zanglamaydigan po&#x27;lat, alyuminiy va guruch — korporativ sovg&#x27;alar uchun eng mashhur materiallar. Metallga o&#x27;ymakorlik qat&#x27;iy va professional ko&#x27;rinadi.</p>\n<p><strong>Mashhur buyumlar:</strong> termoslar, krujkalar, flesh-disklar, breloklar, ruchkalar, zажигalkalar.</p>\n<h3>Yog&#x27;och</h3>\n<p>Tabiiy yog&#x27;och sovg&#x27;alarga iliq, organik xarakter beradi. Yog&#x27;ochga o&#x27;ymakorlik yuzani kuydirish hisobiga kontrastli naqsh yaratadi.</p>\n<p><strong>Mashhur buyumlar:</strong> foto ramkalar, qutichalar, tagliklar, daftarlar.</p>\n<h2>Graver.uz da o&#x27;ymakor sovg&#x27;alar qanday buyurtma qilish mumkin?</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\">Telegram</a> ga yozing yoki +998 77 080 22 88 ga qo&#x27;ng&#x27;iroq qiling</li>\n<li>Vazifani tasvirlab bering: miqdor, material, kerakli buyumlar, muddatlar</li>\n<li>Logotipni vektor formatida yuboring (SVG, AI, EPS)</li>\n<li>Hisob-kitob oling va buyurtmani tasdiqlang</li>\n<li>Biz Toshkent va butun O&#x27;zbekistonga tayyorlab yetkazib beramiz</li>\n</ol>\n<p>10 donadan boshlab B2B-mijozlar bilan ishlaymiz.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Ko&#x27;p so&#x27;raladigan savollar</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><details class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg border border-gray-700\"><summary class=\"px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-white font-medium hover:text-teal-500 transition list-none flex justify-between items-center\">Lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik sovg&#x27;alar haqida ishni qayerdan boshlash kerak?<span class=\"text-teal-500 ml-4 flex-shrink-0\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-6 pb-4 text-gray-400\">Kampaniya maqsadi, maqsadli auditoriya va har bir qabul qiluvchi uchun belgilangan byudjetdan boshlang.</div></details><details class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg border border-gray-700\"><summary class=\"px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer text-white font-medium hover:text-teal-500 transition list-none flex justify-between items-center\">Ishga tushirishni ko&#x27;pincha nima to&#x27;xtatib qo&#x27;yadi?<span class=\"text-teal-500 ml-4 flex-shrink-0\">+</span></summary><div class=\"px-6 pb-4 text-gray-400\">Maketni kech tasdiqlash, segmentlar bo&#x27;yicha ustuvorliklarning yo&#x27;qligi va kelishilmagan logistika rejasi.</div></details></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><d