o'p qirralilik — metall, yog'och, teri, shishada ishlaydi\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Qaysi materiallar o'ymakorlik uchun mos keladi?\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Metall\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Zanglamaydigan po'lat, alyuminiy va guruch — korporativ sovg'alar uchun eng mashhur materiallar. Metallga o'ymakorlik qat'iy va professional ko'rinadi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Mashhur buyumlar:\"}],\" termoslar, krujkalar, flesh-disklar, breloklar, ruchkalar, zажигalkalar.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Yog'och\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Tabiiy yog'och sovg'alarga iliq, organik xarakter beradi. Yog'ochga o'ymakorlik yuzani kuydirish hisobiga kontrastli naqsh yaratadi.\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Mashhur buyumlar:\"}],\" foto ramkalar, qutichalar, tagliklar, daftarlar.\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"children\":\"Graver.uz da o'ymakor sovg'alar qanday buyurtma qilish mumkin?\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"children\":[\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"https://t.me/GraverAdm\",\"children\":\"Telegram\"}],\" ga yozing yoki +998 77 080 22 88 ga qo'ng'iroq qiling\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Vazifani tasvirlab bering: miqdor, material, kerakli buyumlar, muddatlar\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Logotipni vektor formatida yuboring (SVG, AI, EPS)\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Hisob-kitob oling va buyurtmani tasdiqlang\"}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Biz Toshkent va butun O'zbekistonga tayyorlab yetkazib beramiz\"}],\"\\n\"]}],\"\\n\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"10 donadan boshlab B2B-mijozlar bilan ishlaymiz.\"}]]\nb:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-sc